item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens When You Check Your Tim Hortons Roll Up the Rim!
item.description: Introduction to Tim Hortons Roll Up the Rim If you’re a fan of Tim Hortons, then you know that one of the best parts of their coffee is the chance to win some amazing prizes with their Roll Up the Rim contest. Every year, customers get the chance to roll up the rim of their coffee cup and see if they’ve won a prize. It’s a fun way to get a little something extra with your coffee and it’s a great way to show your loyalty to the brand.
